  .flex-video
    iframe width="600" height="450" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/NIbJJi9GHms?rel=0&amp;controls=0&amp;showinfo=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen
  p Existem grandes chances de você já ter visto algo assim:
  .flex-video
    iframe width="600" height="450" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/v246c8wP6_0?rel=0&amp;controls=0&amp;showinfo=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen
